      "customOneOffs": [
        "Bigfoot Nightbane are 7-8 feet (2.1 to 2.4 m) tall and weigh 300-350 pounds (136.5 to 157.5 kg).",
        "+2 on Perception Rolls especially regarding ambushes, hiding and tracking in the wilderness.",
        ", Camouflage and Climbing skills in wooded environments, and +10% to all Wilderness skills.",
        "Automatically starts with the Leave No Trace Talent.",
        "They also tend to eschew high-tech 'gadgets' like cell phones and computers."
      ]
