      "customOneOffs": [
        "Adds +1 to Spell Strength if a magic user.",
        "The character does not get a breath weapon, but can select the Fire Breather Talent at half the normal cost and double the normal damage to Nightlords and the denizens of the Nightlands.",
        "The -2 penalty to dodge applies only when not airborne.",
        "Too large to fit in ordinary vehicles and may have trouble negotiating hallways and staircases inside buildings.",
        "All magic and enchanted weapons, including Dark Blades, ignore the character's Natural A.R. and inflict full damage. Dragon slaying weapons do double damage."
